HEADWORD: Governor general
<hw>Gov"ern*or gen"er*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A governor who has
lieutenant or deputy governors under him; <as>as, the <ex>governor
general</ex> of Canada, of India</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

